reviewText: A beautiful masterpiece work.  The art and the music are so inspiring.  A wonderful tribute to the feminine mystique.  I recommend that all women of wisdom see this gorgeous gift to the divine feminine.

Complete with an amazing soundtrack of heart opening musical insight, this DVD instilled an incredibly deep reverence and awe for the Goddess and for Creation itself.  For many minutes afterward, I had my eyes closed and the inner visions continued to stream upon my own neocortex, filled with metaphysical symbols and insight and an inner experience of the Creative Divine flowing through my own being.... this is a brilliant voyage worth owning and sharing with friends to create a mystical group experience...
